Job Title

: Senior C# Engineer with AWS / Full-Stack Developer

Location

: Remote

Type

: Contract

 

Job Description:

Position Overview:

We are seeking a highly skilled and motivated Senior Software Engineer with expertise in .NET, C#, ASP.NET Core, ReactJS, and cloud technologies such as AWS (including Step Functions, Lambda, API Gateway, and S3).
The ideal candidate must be capable of working independently, taking ownership of projects, and delivering high-quality solutions in a fast-paced environment.
If you are passionate about building scalable, secure, and modern web applications, this role is for you.
 

Key Responsibilities:

Design, develop, and maintain robust, scalable, and high-performance applications using .NET Core, C#, and ASP.NET Core.
Build responsive and interactive user interfaces using ReactJS.
Architect and implement cloud-native solutions using AWS services, including Step Functions, Lambda, API Gateway, S3, and other related services.
Create and maintain infrastructure as code using Terraform for AWS resource provisioning and management.
Develop and consume RESTful APIs, ensuring optimal performance and scalability.
Ensure high-quality code by performing unit testing, code reviews, and adhering to best practices.
Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including product managers, designers, and other developers, to deliver end-to-end solutions.
Debug, troubleshoot, and resolve application and infrastructure issues in a timely manner.
Take full ownership of assigned projects, including gathering requirements, designing solutions, and delivering on commitments with minimal supervision.
Continuously monitor and optimize application performance, security, and reliability.
 

