Hands-on experience with AWS services such as Step Functions, Lambda, API Gateway, and S3.
Experience with Terraform for infrastructure as code and cloud resource management.
Strong understanding of RESTful API design, development, and consumption.
Proficiency in designing and implementing secure, scalable, and maintainable architectures.
